nodes.text: Jaymizu Poh was a Human female Tarisian who lived on Taris during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire.

In 3643 BBY, she and her brother Relus Poh were trying to reclaim land on Taris that belonged to their family, but the area was patrolled by hostile defense droids owned by a group of Togruta who were living in the estate as refugees.
